Titolo: Tax Avoiders

Anno: 1982

Descrizione: Tax Avoiders is a single-player video game for the Atari 2600 released in 1982. It was conceived by Darrell Wagner at Dunhill Electronics; he was billed on the packaging as a "Licensed Tax Consultant and former IRS Revenue Agent". The game was developed by Todd Clark Holm, "an independant [sic] investment advisor, registered with the S.E.C.". Game designed by John Simonds and published by American Videogame.

Genere: Platform 

Valutazione: N/A
